summary: A handsome male Nord preset. Also works as a Ningheim!
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://i750.photobucket.com/albums/xx141/ninjakamihana/Diverse/ScreenShot255.jpg[/img]

A preset for a male Nord character I have been playing with and customizing for a few months. 
Hope you like him!

[i]Edit 1: Turns out he also works great as a Ningheim preset!
You might have to change the face part in the Racemenu if you want to customize him further yourself.[/i]

You will need:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos 
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27815/?]Fine Face Textures for Men by Urshi[/url] (You can try other textures, but he will look very different!)

Recommended:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28363/?]Beards[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]Brows
[/url][url=http://www.ladymoiraine.com/index.php?/forums/forum/304-sam-shape-atlas-for-men/]SAM Body[/url] (NSFW link, you must register to download)
I use the [url=http://www.ladymoiraine.com/index.php?/forums/topic/5916-daren-bless-online-armor-for-sam-v11/]Daren Armor[/url] and [url=http://www.ladymoiraine.com/index.php?/forums/topic/5977-rel-hymnarus-clothing-project-for-sam/]Briefs[/url] in some of the pictures.
author: Kamihana
